# Minimal 风格动画配置

极简风格，使用淡入淡出效果，适用于商务演示。

```json
{
  "metadata": {
    "style": "minimal",
    "page_count": 5,
    "transition_count": 5,
    "element_animation_count": 10
  },
  "transitions": [
    {
      "page_index": 1,
      "type": "fade",
      "duration": 0.8,
      "easing": "linear",
      "params": {
        "opacity_start": 0.0,
        "opacity_end": 1.0
      }
    },
    {
      "page_index": 2,
      "type": "fade",
      "duration": 0.8,
